Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:09.01,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I had lost my way during my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:17.02,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Only my soul was wandering, while I stood still.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:25.28,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}But right now, I'm walking to a distant place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:33.53,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}That's right, ever since I met you on this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:41.96,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}The travellers witnessed the song, the forbidden song,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:52.72,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And I became attached to it as I heard it alone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:01:00.81,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}If the world I saw in my dreams exists somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:09.20,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Let's go search for it, beyond the winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:13.37,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Whether it's a freezing dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:17.58,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A dry midday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:21.75,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A shivering night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:28.00,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}or the ends of the Earth, let's go and see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:40.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:43.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The air is wavering.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:48.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The market is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:51.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:52.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's wavering.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:02:00.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of splashing water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:04.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:06.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In front!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:08.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we've got to fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:10.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there only a single path?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The path we're using is a single one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:18.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think even {\i1}I{\i0} have the confidence to not get lost in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:22.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we run, they'll catch up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:26.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They've let dogs loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:27.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're stupid ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:33.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, cover your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:05.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:09.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you eat as many as you want later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:14.48,Chapter Name Title Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolf and Silent Farewell
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:16.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How did they figure it out, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:17.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that they figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:20.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably went underground and found us by coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:22.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If they had known, they would've pinned us on both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:29.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The Milone Company has sold you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Running is useless now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:34.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we were sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We must've been sold at a high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:46.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're here, they can take out Milone's local branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:49.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, then it must've been quite a high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:53.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a bluff instead of a greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we turn this corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:05.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:06.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where we're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:08.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:17.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn left next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:30.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that, I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:42.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive my sin, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:54.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Repent for your habitual behavior {\i1}before{\i0} your sins!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:04.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:08.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:14.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:19.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:22.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I called for you several times, but you didn't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:28.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:30.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just a bit sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:37.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold on for a bit longer, we're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:39.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:40.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a scent of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you there's a place we can go up, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:54.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:57.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:06:00.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't even notice that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:04.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang on a bit more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:13.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we reach the end of this path, there'll be an exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:15.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:24.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,An old well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:27.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:30.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think it would turn out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:37.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:39.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:42.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:49.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying! Even if I didn't have such ears, I could tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:59.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if it might have been you from the reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:02.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think that it would really be you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:04.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:11.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The one backing the Medioh Company is Count Eirin Dotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:13.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If your dealings take place in wheat country,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:17.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,you can make payments with any coin you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:22.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, the abolishment of the wheat tariff was done by the Count and Medioh Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:26.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,To everyone in the village, it would seem like a blessing from heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:30.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you have merchant acquaintances that would buy wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:32.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You also let the village chief handle the negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:37.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the wheat dealings happen after the harvest festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's leave these piled-up stories for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:44.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:49.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I visited your village, we didn't get to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:53.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You met another fine person though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand her over to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:00.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll present her to the church,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:02.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and then break away from the old era.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:07.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we hand her over, we can also take out Milone Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:10.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we can abolish the tariff,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:14.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,our village will gain a massive profit from wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:18.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That also goes for merchants who handle our wheat, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:23.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We were thankful that you bought our wheat, even though the village
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:25.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,was suffering from the tariff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:30.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your preference for buying wheat from us was as if you really recognized us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:36.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's succeed together and open a shop in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:40.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a merchant, you can at least recognize the losses and gains here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:43.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to accomplish my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:09:00.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, keeping a promise is the first step to becoming a good merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:08.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fate I have, since a weird wolf that I picked up wished to return to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:13.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And I also made a contract to accompany her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:16.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't break contracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:18.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Our time together was short.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:27.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewells are part of being a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:37.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You can kill the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:39.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to capture the woman alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:45.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to come, then come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:54.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The dagger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:58.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It might hurt a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please endure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:17.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sucking his blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:30.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't falter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:33.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just a girl that's possess-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:40.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:45.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:39.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,God is always like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:41.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Always...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Always unfair! {lul pwned}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:12:59.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Horo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:38.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:41.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:53.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you think the clothes you tore apart cost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:57.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care whether you're a god or whatever, I'll have you pay me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:02.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The 50 coins you earned aren't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:07.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years do you think it took me to save up the money to buy those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:10.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll chase you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:13.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll chase you all the way to the forest in the north!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:28.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:57.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you awakened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:02.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How is your wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:05.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fine, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:11.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us for putting you in danger because of our ineptitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:12.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:15.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was because of my companion in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:21.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fortunate that the disturbance ended underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:24.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone had seen that form,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:27.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,the head and branch offices might have been set on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I got a report from one of my subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:40.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who found you said that a large wolf wouldn't hand you over until I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:44.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So where is Horo now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:49.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,After carrying you here, she left without saying where she was headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How did the dealings go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:20.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to obtain the rights that Medioh Company wants the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:22.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:26.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We had gathered three hundred and seven thousand, one hundred and twelve coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:30.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The king had intended to devalue the coins quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:35.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, we were able to purchase them outright for 350,000 coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:38.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,350,000 coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:43.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,According to our contract with you, you would receive half of our profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:45.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:48.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:50.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:17:00.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,120 coins, that's half of our profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:04.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Only this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:07.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The fee for the transportation of the coins,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:09.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,the tariff that accompanies it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:12.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and the handling charge for the contract itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:18.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A contract handling charge? I can't believe they'd charge that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:20.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A purveyor to the government probably gave them a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:25.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for obtaining the rights, we thought we'd try to recover from the loss
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:26.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,of buying the coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:30.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was something we couldn't foresee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:33.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an unfortunate outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:38.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforeseen events are part of our trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:39.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:42.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforeseen events...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:45.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,...can also turn out for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:55.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the Medioh Company really wanted the rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:18:00.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, we know they were gathering coins under the assumption they would lower in value.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:03.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same thing as having debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:07.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they had wanted to do business where they could reliably anticipate their profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:11.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They had promptly offered us a price for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:13.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But, 1000 coins is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:15.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's quite cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:17.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like your pay in silver coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:20.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like to exchange it for goods instead, we could prepare it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:22.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have pepper?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's light and it won't be unwieldy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:32.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be winter soon, and if there are more meat dishes, the price will rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:35.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:36.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:39.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered a play I had read recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:41.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Play?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:42.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:47.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a merrymaking play by the church aimed at companies so that they trade in moderation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:52.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Before a rich merchant, a demon appears and says to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.39,0:18:57.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bring the most delicious human to me, or else I will eat you."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:19:02.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The merchant, valuing his life, offered the demon young maids and fat men,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:04.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but the demon was not satisfied with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:07.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,After scouring the town for a delicious-looking human,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:11.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,he finally found a boy that smelled of honey and milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:14.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He immediately offered the boy to the demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:17.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but the boy said to the demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:20.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,"Is the most delicious human really before you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.73,0:19:24.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, day after day, this man's fat soul
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:28.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,is being seasoned with spices, and it's finally showing its effects!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:37.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I had just imagined you all fattened and about to be eaten by the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:41.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like it if my body was seasoned with spices and started showing its effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:42.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:49.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on, I'd like to maintain good relations with a great merchant like you, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:52.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:54.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I have some work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:05.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to be an invoice addressed to you, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:11.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember trading for these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the unloading place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:28.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, um, go to the end of the hall and turn right-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:30.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.13,0:20:33.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please move out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:34.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:37.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,One robe and set of clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,a silk handkerchief,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:41.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,traveling shoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:43.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,a tortoiseshell comb,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:49.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and lastly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:56.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A large quantity of apples!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:21:00.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In all, it comes to 140 coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:01.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:04.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:18.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd be able to pay my debt until I reached the northern forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:23.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:48.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you back when I reach my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:53.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:02.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolf and spice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.69,0:22:19.67,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven apples on the witch's tree
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:25.05,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,With seven seeds to plant inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:30.23,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,In spring time I grew a magic song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.23,0:22:32.97,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Then skipping along,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:35.53,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I sang the song to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.53,0:22:40.96,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I look at the world through apple eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:46.29,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And cut myself a slice of sunshine pie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.29,0:22:51.63,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I danced with the peanuts for the flies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.63,0:22:54.26,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Till someone had told me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:57.32,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,To say hello for every good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:23:02.28,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw some sugar stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:07.37,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put them in a jar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.37,0:23:09.94,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.94,0:23:13.38,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:17.24,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little wolf inside a cart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.24,0:23:18.59,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,You say,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:22.88,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And off I go from June to May
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:28.77,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:32.42,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.54,0:23:43.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and Righteous Scale
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.50,0:23:49.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and Righteous Scale
